{
  "text": "Measurement of serum periostin. We performed a human periostin ELISA assay using 2 rat anti-human periostin mAbs (clones no. SS18A and SS17B), as previously reported [CITATION_1] . See Supplemental Methods for details.",
  "correct_citation": {
